---
title: Soy & Sichuan Steak with Garlic Rice & Veggies
description: That's right, we're taking steak and three veg into new territory. First, we're flavouring the steak with soy sauce and Sichuan garlic paste, then we're pan-frying all three veggies and adding a bed of garlic rice. Simple, yet sensational!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dcc8c5b74d9cb456e2a1f08-3c56a8c5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/soy-sichuan-steak-5dcc8c5b74d9cb456e2a1f08-dfcb23d7.pdf
